videos.description: Eva Hodgson drives and takes the bump as she is able to put down an and-1 layup to help North Carolina take a 48-47 lead over Louisville.

videos.description: Mykasa Robinson comes up big for Louisville as she helps them regain the lead at the end of the third quarter by knocking down a buzzer-beating 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Mykasa Robinson nails a buzzer-beater to end the 3rd) 2022/02/17 ESHEET
